&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;About the Role:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced Audio Director to lead the sonic vision for our horror game experiences. This role blends creative leadership, technical audio expertise, and cross-disciplinary collaboration to craft deeply immersive, emotionally charged player experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate understands how sound shapes fear, tension, pacing, and psychological storytelling in interactive media. You know when silence is more powerful than music, how to build anticipation through environmental sound, and how to create audio systems that react dynamically to player behavior.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will oversee all aspects of audio direction including music, sound design, VO implementation, interactive systems, mixing, outsourcing, and team leadership across multiple projects or live content pipelines.&lt;/p&gt;
