&lt;h3&gt;Leadership &amp;amp; Collaboration&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead internal audio teams as well as external composers, sound houses, VO vendors, and freelance partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide clear creative feedback, mentorship, and production direction to the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help build scalable workflows for rapid iteration in production environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in milestone planning, risk assessment, and production prioritization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Creative Audio Direction&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and maintain the overall sonic identity for horror-focused game experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop audio strategies that reinforce gameplay tension, emotional pacing, atmosphere, and narrative beats.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise implementation of adaptive music systems, environmental audio, creature vocalization, jump scares, ambience, and psychological audio cues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Creative, Narrative, Design, and Art leadership to ensure cohesive player immersion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Sound Design &amp;amp; Systems&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee creation and integration of high-quality sound effects, ambience, Foley, VO, and music.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide implementation pipelines using Unreal Engine and Metasounds.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Engineering and Technical Audio teams on interactive audio systems, optimization, and runtime performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish audio standards, mix targets, loudness consistency, and platform compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Production &amp;amp; Pipeline&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage audio scope, scheduling, outsourcing, and deliverable tracking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure high-quality implementation within technical and memory constraints.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support live updates, seasonal content, cinematic moments, and gameplay-driven audio needs.&lt;/li&gt;
