&lt;li&gt;Enforce community guidelines and policies, ensuring a positive and safe gaming environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with the moderation team to manage and resolve conflicts and disputes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Community Advocacy:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
