&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with product managers and developers to align game features with community expectations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Community Growth:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop strategies to increase the size and engagement of the gaming community on both Discord and social media channels.&lt;/li&gt;
